3186   1      
3187   1          //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
3188   1          // Precise formula of Chrage Pump Current depends on DPM, resistor, and band.                   //
3189   1          // If VCO band = 'b00, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (778 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                          //
3190   1          // If VCO band = 'b01, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (1340 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                         //
3191   1          // If VCO band = 'b10, Icp = (700 * M * 2 * pi) / (1880 * 0x01C1[7:5]).                         //
